Motion Amplify requires working installation of matlab engine for python.
Install instructions can be found here:
https://se.mathworks.com/help/matlab/matlab_external/install-the-matlab-engine-for-python.html

If using virtualenvironment:
https://se.mathworks.com/help/matlab/matlab_external/install-matlab-engine-api-for-python-in-nondefault-locations.html
Where *installdir* should point to virtualenvironment folder.
